1. Your comment

I now see more complaints. The latest rule in uBO is receiving mixed feedback at least on Brave, so I changed to https://listauthorschat.slack.com/archives/C010N14G4TF/p1723225777981599?thread_ts=1683754186.016929&cid=C010N14G4TF which is more time-tested. Tested with Chrome ext 4.4.22 the rule is working fine on my end. I'm not sure about the `replace` rule for Firefox, in particular why `\$2` escape is needed.

